results.story: Inspired by motorsport, the Scuderia Ferrari x PUMA Roma Toddler Black dresses the sleek low-top in a leather upper with perforated Formstrip branding. A low-cut mesh collar combines with a foam-lined leather tongue to provide a comfortable fit. A yellow Ferrari badge decorates the lateral heel, while PUMAs jumping cat logo adorns the woven tongue tag and heel overlay. The sneaker rides on a black EVA midsole and color-matched herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

Roma Basic Summer Infant 'Castlerock'
results.story: The PUMA Roma Basic Summer Infant Castlerock delivers a neutral colorway of the training shoe designed to celebrate Italys 1968 Euro Cup championship in Rome. Shaped for little feet, the sneaker makes use of a grey textile upper with tonal synthetic leather overlays. The monotone finish is interrupted by a white leather Formstrip and PUMA Roma inscribed in metallic gold on the lateral quarter panel. An unexpected pop of neon yellow lands on the foam midsole, supported underfoot by a tacky gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Roma Basic Summer Infant 'Black Star Sapphire'
results.story: Drawn from the brands 1960s archive, the PUMA Roma Basic Summer Infant Black Star Sapphire presents a scaled-down version of the retro trainer for little feet. Black textile is utilized on the upper, reinforced with tonal leather overlays and accented with a contrasting blue Formstrip. A matching blue heel tab displays PUMAs signature jumping cat logo. The low-top rides on a two-tone foam midsole, reinforced with a gum rubber outsole that extends up and around the toe.

results.name: Roma Basic Summer Infant 'Pink Lady Poppy Red'
results.story: The PUMA Roma Basic Summer Infant Pink Lady Poppy Red showcases bright candy colors on a scaled-down version of the vintage silhouette. A vibrant pink finish is applied to a textile upper with tonal leather overlays at the toe and heel. Branding elements include a scarlet leather Formstrip and PUMA Roma stamped in metallic gold on the lateral quarter panel. Underfoot, a herringbone-tread gum rubber outsole delivers grippy traction.

results.name: Ralph Sampson Low Infant 'Time4Change - Peachskin'
results.story: The PUMA Ralph Sampson Low Infant Peachskin is drawn from the Time4Change collection, featuring kids shoes and apparel made with sustainable materials. This scaled-down iteration of the vintage hoops shoe replaces traditional lace closure with dual hook-and-loop straps. They secure a peach-hued recycled cotton upper, fortified with tonal synthetic leather at the toe and heel. Time4Change branding adorns a midfoot overlay constructed from recycled polyurethane.

results.name: Ralph Sampson Low Infant 'Time4Change - Peacoat'
results.story: The PUMA Ralph Sampson Low Infant Peacoat is taken from the brands Time4Change collection, an eco-friendly assortment of apparel and footwear built with sustainable materials. This mini version of the retro hoops shoe features dual hook-and-loops straps and a navy textile upper constructed from recycled cotton. The sneakers uniform palette is enlivened by a striped detailing on the collar lining and Ralph Sampsons gold-foil signature on the lateral quarter panel. Time4Change branding adorns an accompanying midfoot overlay.

results.name: Cruise Rider Infant 'Viridian Green'
results.story: The PUMA Cruise Rider Infant Viridian Green combines exaggerated tooling with a layered, retro-inspired build. Emerald mesh on the upper is fortified with overlays in textile and synthetic suede, as well as a hint of patent leather wrapped around the heel. The sneaker is mounted on a stacked injection-molded EVA midsole, good for lightweight cushioning with each step. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a waffle-style tread for reliable traction.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'Black White'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant Black White delivers a scaled-down version of the classic silhouette, featuring a lightly refreshed build made for the 21st century. The upper is constructed from the sneakers eponymous material, unheard of for use in a basketball shoe in 1968  the year the low-top originally released. In addition to an off-white suede Formstrip, contrast-hued branding elements include an archival tongue tag and a gold-foil PUMA Suede wordmark on the lateral side panel.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'High Risk Red'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant High Risk Red brings back the 1968 basketball shoe in a lightly redesigned iteration made for little feet. The upper is immersed in an eye-catching shade of crimson, contrasted by an off-white suede Formstrip and metallic gold PUMA Suede branding. A removable foam sockliner combines with a textile-lined interior to deliver a comfortable fit. Underfoot, a non-marking rubber outsole provides durable traction.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'Black'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant Black retrieves a vintage basketball shoe from the brands late 60s archive, scaled down and dipped in ebony for little feet. The one-note finish on the suede upper is disrupted by the sneakers branding hits, including a woven tongue tag and PUMA Suede stamped in gold lettering on the lateral side panel. The sneaker is mounted on a matching black rubber cupsole, featuring textured sidewalls and a grid-like traction pattern underfoot.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'Pink Lady'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant Pink Lady features a pastel finish throughout the sneakers eponymous upper. The subtle pink hue is contrasted by an off-white suede Formstrip and a PUMA Suede callout in metallic gold lettering. Soft textile lines the interior, which pairs with a removable foam sockliner to provide a comfortable fit for growing feet. The rubber cupsole is undergirded with a traction pattern originally developed for the hardwood.

results.name: Suede Classic 21 Infant 'Peacoat'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic 21 Infant Peacoat features a classic two-tone palette on a scaled down edition of the vintage hoops shoe originally released in 1968. Lightly refreshed for the 21st century, the low-top makes use of a navy suede upper with a contrasting off-white Formstrip. A PUMA Suede wordmark in gold foil lettering shines on the lateral quarter panel. Soft textile lines the interior, while a removable Kinder-Fit sockliner provides step-in comfort.
